===Etymology===
From {{etyl|ang}} {{term|spadu|lang=ang}}, {{term|spada|lang=ang}}, of {{proto|Germanic||head=Germanic}} origin. Cognate with {{ofs}} {{term|spada|lang=ofs}}, {{osx}} {{term|spado|lang=osx}}, {{de}} {{term|Spaten|lang=de}}. Ultimately from {{proto|Indo-European|spə-dh-|lang=en}}, whence also Ancient Greek {{term|σπάθη||blade|tr=spathē|lang=grc}}, Hittite {{term||išpatar|spear}} {{rfscript|Cuneiform}}.

